      <odd id="aspace_054d7fdd8b78bd9a11f2f33c960d97dc">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-A (YRG 38-A), Records documenting administration of Yale athletic and physical education programs.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_fae143374603af28a5b0c2bb3e0e2439">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Department of Athletics, Yale University, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
